<item>
            <title>[ZOOKEEPER-117] threading issues in Leader election</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/ZOOKEEPER-117</link>
                <project id="12310801" key="ZOOKEEPER">ZooKeeper</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Leader.lead() creates a new thread that can never terminate (short of restarting vm)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;naked notifyall in lead() method - what is the condition variable? Best if set inside the sync block&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12402144">ZOOKEEPER-117</key>
